1463
01:19:29,416 --> 01:19:32,000
Mike, awak tak perlu
jawab soalan itu. Bantahan.

1464
01:19:32,458 --> 01:19:34,833
Saya dapat dengar awak tadi, En. Gary.

1465
01:19:34,833 --> 01:19:37,875
